<topic id="editing-JSON-schema">
  <title>Editing JSON Schema Documents</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>JSON Schema</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_alw_dgc_2rb"><ph keyref="product"/> offers powerful tools that allow you to design,
      develop, and edit JSON Schemas. These tools include:<ul id="ul_b4q_zhc_2rb">
        <li id="li_c4q_zhc_2rb"><xref
            href="json-schema-editor.dita#json-schema-editor/section_uw2_cxr_1nb"
              ><uicontrol>Text</uicontrol> editing mode</xref> (packed full of editing helpers)</li>
        <li id="li_u4k_c3c_2rb"><xref href="json-schema-design-mode.dita">Schema
              <uicontrol>Design</uicontrol> mode</xref> (a visual, intuitive schema diagram
          editor)<?oxy_comment_start author="Octavian" timestamp="20211007T050941+0000" comment="Add also Grid and Author pages here."?></li><?oxy_comment_end?>
        <li id="li_srf_g3c_2rb" product="developer editor"><xref
            href="json-schema-documentation-generator.dita">JSON Schema documentation tool</xref>
          for producing high quality output</li>
        <li id="li_pyy_g3c_2rb"><xref href="json-schema-instance-generator.dita">JSON Schema
            instance generator</xref> for producing JSON Schema documents from a JSON file</li>
        <li id="li_pgq_33c_2rb"><xref href="xsd-to-json-schema-converter.dita">XSD to JSON Schema
            converter tool</xref> for producing a JSON Schema from an XML schema </li>
      </ul></p>
    <p id="p_sfg_cgk_54b">This section describes the features included in <ph keyref="product"/> for
      editing JSON Schema documents and how to use them.</p>
    <section id="section_v54_rr5_ypb">
      <title>Resources</title>
      <p id="p_w54_rr5_ypb">For more information about the JSON support in <ph keyref="product"/>,
        see the following resources:<ul id="ul_bzc_455_ypb">
          <li id="li_czc_455_ypb">Webinar: <xref
              href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/events/2020/webinar_json_and_json_schema_support_in_oxygen_xml_editor.html"
              format="html" scope="external"><b>JSON and JSON Schema Support in
            Oxygen</b></xref>.</li>
          <li id="li_ljr_r55_ypb">Video: <xref href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IEzaPRPHmGc"
              format="html" scope="external"><b>Introducing JSON Schema Design Mode</b></xref>.</li>
          <li id="li_ljr_r55_ypb2">Video: <xref href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wgIkagwSDrU"
              format="html" scope="external"><b>JSON Editing</b></xref>.</li>
          <li id="li_if5_gv5_ypb">Video: <xref href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k3LHBU01GFI"
              format="html" scope="external"><b>JSON Tools in Oxygen</b></xref></li>
        </ul></p>
    </section>
